Santander Chile Will Invest $380 Million, CEO Tells Mercurio

-- B y   J a m e s   A t t w o o d
-- 
2011-03-21T11:48:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/santander-chile-will-invest-380-million-ceo-tells-mercurio.html
  Banco Santander Chile (BSAN)  plans to
invest $380 million through 2013 to open at least 30 branches,
Chief Executive Officer Claudio Melandri told El Mercurio.  About 42 percent will be invested this year, the Santiago-
based newspaper quoted Melandri as saying in an interview
published today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Attwood at 
 jattwood3@bloomberg.net  